text: Maryna Slutskaya (born 9 July 1991) is a Belarusian judoka. She is the 2017 European gold medalist in the +78 kg division. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian female judoka Category:Universiade medalists in judo Category:Universiade bronze medalists for Belarus Category:European Games competitors for Belarus Category:Judoka at the 2015 European Games Category:Judoka at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games medalists in judo Category:European Games gold medalists for Belarus Category:Medalists at the 2013 Summer Universiade
